# Marque Cheat Sheet

Everything below is shown as **Code** and **Preview** side by side.

@callout .info
	This page covers all built-in directives currently parsed by Marque,
	plus markdown enhancements supported by the renderer.
@end callout

@divider

## 1) Row + Card

@row row-card-basic
	@card .accent
		### Code

		```mq
		@row features
			@card .accent
				## Fast
				Build pages quickly.
			@end card

			@card
				## Simple
				Static output only.
			@end card
		@end row
		```
	@end card

	@card
		### Preview

		@row features
			@card .accent
				## Fast
				Build pages quickly.
			@end card

			@card
				## Simple
				Static output only.
			@end card
		@end row
	@end card
@end row row-card-basic

## 2) Card Modifiers

@row card-mods
	@card .accent
		### Code

		```mq
		@row card-mods
			@card .accent
				Accent card
			@end card
			@card .accent2
				Accent2 card
			@end card
			@card .ghost
				Ghost card
			@end card
			@card .dark
				Dark card
			@end card
		@end row
		```
	@end card

	@card
		### Preview

		@row card-mods
			@card .accent
				Accent card
			@end card
			@card .accent2
				Accent2 card
			@end card
			@card .ghost
				Ghost card
			@end card
			@card .dark
				Dark card
			@end card
		@end row
	@end card
@end row card-mods

