## 5) Tabs + Tab

@row tabs-demo
	@card .accent
		### Code

		```mq
		@tabs workflows
			@tab Install
				npm install
			@end tab

			@tab Build
				marque build .
			@end tab

			@tab Serve
				marque serve .
			@end tab
		@end tabs
		```
	@end card

	@card
		### Preview

		@tabs workflows
			@tab Install
				npm install
			@end tab

			@tab Build
				marque build .
			@end tab

			@tab Serve
				marque serve .
			@end tab
		@end tabs
	@end card
@end row tabs-demo

## 6) Steps + Step

@row steps-demo
	@card .accent
		### Code

		```mq
		@steps publish
			@step one
				## Write
				Create content in pages/*.mq.
			@end step

			@step two
				## Build
				Run marque build .
			@end step

			@step three
				## Deploy
				Upload dist/.
			@end step
		@end steps
		```
	@end card

	@card
		### Preview

		@steps publish
			@step one
				## Write
				Create content in pages/*.mq.
			@end step

			@step two
				## Build
				Run marque build .
			@end step

			@step three
				## Deploy
				Upload dist/.
			@end step
		@end steps
	@end card
@end row steps-demo

