## 9) Generic Custom Blocks

Unknown directives are rendered as generic containers: `@tag` -> `.mq-tag`.

@row generic-demo
	@card .accent
		### Code

		```mq
		@promo .accent launch
			## Custom Block
			This becomes .mq-promo.accent
		@end promo launch
		```
	@end card

	@card
		### Preview

		@promo .accent launch
			## Custom Block
			This becomes .mq-promo.accent
		@end promo launch
	@end card
@end row generic-demo

## 10) Markdown Enhancements

@row markdown-plus
	@card .accent
		### Code

		```md
		:badge[Stable]{.ok}

		@[Primary CTA](/start.html){.primary}
		@[Download](/download.zip){.download}

		[Read docs →](/docs.html)
		```
	@end card

	@card
		### Preview

		:badge[Stable]{.ok}

		@[Primary CTA](/start.html){.primary}
		@[Download](/download.zip){.download}

		[Read docs →](/docs.html)
	@end card
@end row markdown-plus

## 11) Frontmatter (Page Controls)

@row frontmatter-demo
	@card .accent
		### Code

		```yaml
		---
		title: Cheat Sheet
		nav: cheat sheet
		theme: default
		layout: topnav
		width: wide
		---
		```
	@end card

	@card
		### Preview

		- `title`: display title and document title segment.
		- `nav`: output slug used for generated filename.
		- `theme`: page-level theme override.
		- `layout`: page-level layout override.
		- `width`: `narrow|normal|wide|full`, numeric `%`, or explicit `%`.
		- Order/labels come from `summary.mq`.
	@end card
@end row frontmatter-demo
